FBIS4-42286 "drweu105_h_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-105 Daily Report 29 May 1994 GERMANY Russia Seeks Compensation for Former Properties Russia Seeks Compensation for Former Properties LD2905104594 Berlin N-TV in German 1000 GMT 29 May 94 LD2905104594 Berlin N-TV German BFN [Text] Russia is lodging claims worth billions [currency unspecified] against Germany in respect of property in eastern Germany, according to FOCUS magazine. Moscow is demanding the restitution of at least 1,200 buildings and plots of land, including prime sites in the most expensive areas of Berlin, Dresden, and Leipzig. More than 100 sites were legally acquired in the 1950's by the Soviet Foreign Trade Office.
